1
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:02,900
Yesterday, the songs I asked you to choose from —

2
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,540
do you have a favorite?

3
00:02:05,300 --> 00:02:06,700
Which one did you decide on in the end?

4
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:08,940
I —

5
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,600
I want to sing my own song.

6
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,480
No, it's not that your songs are bad. I just —

7
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:14,660
I'm afraid people might think you —

8
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,700
think about the relationship between us —

9
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:18,680
I understand.

10
00:02:21,380 --> 00:02:22,940
Let's do it your way, then.

11
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,600
You don't understand at all.

12
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:29,080
What did you say?

13
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,080
Nothing.

14
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,540
It's nothing.

15
00:02:30,540 --> 00:02:31,340
I'm leaving first.

16
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,100
Wait.

17
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,000
I arranged the music for you.

18
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,740
I made some adjustments in a few places.

19
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,180
Have a listen.

20
00:02:59,340 --> 00:03:00,480
It really feels different.

21
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:04,340
Before, I always felt the melody was a bit sad.

22
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,740
Now,

23
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:09,940
I can hear a hint of glimmer in it.

24
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,940
The foundation of this song is very good.

25
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:17,700
So

26
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,940
let's perfect it together.

27
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,280
Okay.

28
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,600
I'm going to change something here.

29
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,440
Xiao Yao.

30
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:36,280
What time did you leave yesterday?

31
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,680
You —

32
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:41,080
don't remember at all?

33
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:49,480
I kind of blacked out from drinking.

34
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:54,180
I left after I woke up.

35
00:05:03,780 --> 00:05:04,780
Good thing it wasn't real.

36
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:06,380
What did you just say?

37
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,180
Never mind, it's nothing.

38
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,720
Let's record the song.

39
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,600
Not bad.

40
00:06:59,300 --> 00:06:59,940
Nice one.

41
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:00,480
Old Zhou.

42
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,600
Not bad.

43
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,500
The timbre is very good.

44
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,680
The voice is also very pure.

45
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:05,940
You have good taste.

46
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,900
No wonder you're Teacher Zhou's assistant.

47
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,600
Teacher Zhou really has good taste.

48
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,300
Xiao Yao,

49
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,540
you passed the preliminary selection.

50
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,780
What preliminary selection?

51
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:24,540
Hey.

52
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,200
Who are you?

53
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,100
Speak.

54
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:29,180
Hey.

55
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:48,100
You participated in Star River Music's selection.

56
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:49,720
Hmm.

57
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,700
Didn't you say you wouldn't sing anymore?

58
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:55,780
So

59
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:59,000
why did you agree to take part?

60
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:04,000
Is it because of him?

61
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,640
Why can he do it

62
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:12,600
after all these years?

63
00:08:13,540 --> 00:08:15,080
Haven't I done enough for you?

64
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,080
That's not it.

65
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,800
You know I've always been grateful to you.

66
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,600
What I want has never been your gratitude.

67
00:08:23,740 --> 00:08:24,740
All these years,

68
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:27,880
it seems I've never been able to enter your heart.

69
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,840
Someone who suddenly appears —

70
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:31,100
so easily, he just —

71
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:32,640
He is not someone who suddenly appeared.

72
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:34,900
He is, from long ago,

73
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:36,540
a beam of light that has lived in my heart.

74
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,540
There was a time I thought

75
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:42,700
it would never shine again.

76
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,580
I want to try,

77
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,700
if it can be conveyed through music.

78
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,700
I also want to tell

79
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:57,180
those who may be going through darkness:

80
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,680
even if the light is very faint,

81
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:03,000
as long as one person can feel it,

82
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,180
that is enough.

83
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:07,600
You like him,

84
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,640
don't you?

85
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,080
Yes.

86
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,080
What about me?

87
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:17,000
What am I to you?

88
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,280
You are my most trusted friend.

89
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,500
You are my family.

90
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:25,800
Always have been.

91
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:30,500
And that will never change.

92
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,240
Li Xingyao,

93
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,940
I never dared hope that you would like me.

94
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:45,140
But your easy compromise for him

95
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,940
makes my desperate pleading

96
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,140
seem utterly worthless.

97
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,640
You —

98
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:56,540
have betrayed my true feelings.

99
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,380
Xingyao,

100
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:34,320
are you hungry?

101
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:44,040
The little sidekick is here delivering food again, huh?

102
00:10:44,580 --> 00:10:45,880
Who said you could eat it?

103
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:47,880
Brother Qiang.

104
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:48,340
Brother Qiang.

105
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:50,600
Itching for a beating again, are you?

106
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,140
Get lost

107
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,020
Are you okay?

108
00:10:58,280 --> 00:10:58,700
Xingyao,

109
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,400
don't be afraid.

110
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,920
Since you're willing to stay with him,

111
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,380
then I'll grant your wish.

112
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,340
Beat him up!

113
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:05,780
Stop hitting him!

114
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,420
Stop!

115
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:12,580
You like him.

116
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,100
What about me?

117
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,820
What am I to you?

118
00:11:39,140 --> 00:11:39,680
Hey.

119
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:42,200
I —

120
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,100
want to see you.

121
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:01,940
What happened?

122
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,540
Because of Xiu Jie.

123
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:09,100
He probably can't be friends with me anymore.

124
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:12,800
Because of what?

125
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:25,680
Is he that important to you?

126
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,200
In my darkest days,

127
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,180
he tried very hard to help me.

128
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,540
When I was hungry,

129
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,140
he would secretly bring me food.

130
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:38,980
When I was beaten,

131
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,280
he would block in front of me with his body.

132
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:47,740
If it weren't for him,

133
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:50,640
I probably would have

134
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,340
not been able to hold on long ago.

135
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:59,840
We've long been used to each other's presence.

136
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,880
But this time,

137
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:05,960
I might really lose him.

138
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:24,200
Suddenly,

139
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:28,340
I really hate this thing called time.

140
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,980
I'll go get the car first.

141
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:35,980
Wait for me here.

142
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:56,180
Do you really not remember?

143
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,980
Or do you not want to remember?

144
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,300
This is my bedroom.

145
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:18,940
You'll be staying here for the time being.

146
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:20,700
Don't overthink it.

147
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,200
What about you?

148
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:49,280
I'll just sleep in the guest room.

149
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:54,580
I still have work to finish.

150
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:56,280
Get some rest early.

151
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,300
Do you hate me that much?

152
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:14,800
What about you?

153
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:54,740
Xiao Yao.

154
00:17:58,780 --> 00:17:59,580
Xiao Yao.

155
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:01,080
Don't be afraid.

156
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,600
With me here, no one will bully you.

157
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,080
Xiao Yao.

158
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:19,540
What kind of terrible things did he experience?

159
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,180
Xiao Yao,

160
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,960
on the table are the daily necessities and clothes

161
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,080
I prepared for you.

162
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,040
Later I'll come back to pick you up for some good food,

163
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:38,280
and then we'll go practice together.

164
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:15,800
Brother Jing'an.

165
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:18,080
You don't actually hate me, do you?
